<h1>Welcome to the IMOS Ocean Portal</h1>
<div id="welcome" class="welcome">
<p>This portal is the primary access point for search, discovery, access and download of data collected by the 
Integrated Marine Observing System (IMOS), an Australian Government Research Infrastructure project. 
You can obtain full information about IMOS via the <a class="external" title="IMOS home page" href="http://www.imos.org.au" target="_blank">IMOS Webpage</a>.</p>
<p>The portal provides two ways of discovering IMOS data, either through a map interface, or by searching our metadata catalogue.</p>
